				</div>
				<div class="newsD-article-title">
					<h2>2024年招聘疼痛科医生公告</h2>
					<p style="font-size:14px;">汉中市第一医院（汉中市妇女儿童医院）官网&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">2024-06-25 14:24:55</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;来源：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阅读量：14721</p>
				</div>
				<div class="newsD-article-content">
					<p>
						<p style="margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 29px">汉中市铁路中心医院</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 29px">招聘疼痛科医生的公告</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">我院因工作需要，拟招聘疼痛科医生</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">1</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">名</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">，欢迎符合条件的人员报名。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、招聘原则</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF">1.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">坚持面向社会、公开招聘。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;line-height: 29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF">2.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">坚持公开、平等、竞争、择优的原则。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">二</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">、招聘</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">岗位及</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">条件</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">（一）基本条件</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">1.遵纪守法，诚实守信，热爱本职工作、具有高度的责任心和敬业精神。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">2.具有岗位所需的专业知识和技能条件，具有良好的思想道德修养、较强的团队意识和协作精神。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">3.五官端正，口齿清晰，语言表达流畅。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">4.身体健康，无传染病及慢性疾病。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">5.与其他单位无劳动关系。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">6.年龄不超过35周岁。</span></span></p><p style="margin-right:0;text-indent:21px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 21px">（二）招聘岗位及资格条件</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">汉中本部疼痛科医生</span><span style="font-family:宋体">1名，要求本科及以上学历，针灸推拿专业、中医骨伤专业或临床医学专业。有中医专业或外科专业医师执业证书者、有住院医师规培合格证者、有硕士学位证者优先。</span></span></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:42px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 21px">三、报名与资格审查</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">1.报名方式和报名地点：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span style="font-family:宋体">1）报名方式：现场报名或线上报名均可。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span style="font-family:宋体">2）现场报名地点：汉中市铁路中心医院人事科－医院行政楼（4号楼）2层。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-size: 19px; background: #FFFFFF; font-family: 宋体;">（3）线上报名邮箱：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #000000; font-size: 19px; background: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: underline;">tlzxyyrsk@163.com</span><span style="font-size: 19px; background: #FFFFFF; font-family: 宋体;">。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">2.报名时间：2024年6月25日至2024年7月5日(每日早8:00-12:00，14:30-17:00，6月29日早8:00-12:00）。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">3.报名所需资料</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span style="font-family:宋体">1）填写完整的《报名表》（见附件）；（2）居民有效身份证原件及复印件；（3）（第一学历至最高学历）毕业证、学位证原件及复印件；（4）（第一学历至最高学历）学历查询结果《学历证书电子注册备案表》（以中国高等教育学生信息网http://www.chsi.com.cn的查询结果为准）打印版一份；（5）岗位所需证书原件及复印件；（6）一寸正面免冠彩色近照1张（底色不限，贴于报名表）；（7）有工作经验者提供岗位所需相关证明。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">线上报名请将以上证证资料的电子版发到线上报名邮箱。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 21px">四、报名初筛及考试安排</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span style="font-family:宋体">1）报名初筛：本次招聘岗位为疼痛科医生岗位，按照《执业医师法》临床医生需执证上岗，本次报名后会进行初筛。如报名人员中，有相应专业医师执业证的人数为N,当N</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">≧</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">3人时，仅在有医师执业证书的人中举行招聘考试。如N小于3时,有医师执业证书的N人全部进入面试，再从无执业证的人员中通过笔试择优选拔(3-N)人，一同进入面试。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">(2)考试安排：招聘考试公告（附进入笔试、面试人员名单）将在报名结束3天内在医院官网http://www.hzstlzxyy.com发布。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 21px">五、福利待遇</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">1.本次招聘用工性质为聘用合同制。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">2.工资结构实行基本工资+绩效工资的工资结构。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">3.社保：按国家规定办理养老保险、医疗保险（含大病保险和生育保险）、工伤保险、失业保险。</span></span></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:42px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: #FF0000;font-size: 21px">六、咨询电话</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">汉中市铁路中心医院人事科</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">0916-2212561。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:宋体">附件：招聘报名表</span></span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;background: #FFFFFF">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>						附件：<a class="download" href='/home/plugs/download/id/1546.html'>附件：招聘报名表.docx</a>
																	</p>
					<!--<a href="#">返回</a>-->
				</div>
				<div class="expert_details_bottom">
										<span>上一篇：</span><a href="/article/notice/1155.html" class="toe">汉中市铁路中心医院肛周熏洗治疗仪采购项目磋商结果公告</a>
										<span>下一篇：</span><a href="/article/notice/1157.html" class="toe">汉中市铁路中心医院 6月招聘医学检验工作人员拟聘人选公示</a>
									</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
